Usage: ./vm_champs/corewar [-dump X -v X -n X]
#### TEXT OUTPUT MODE ##########################################################
		-dump X	: Dumps memory after X cycles then exits. X is an integer.
		-n    X	: Set a player's id to X. X is an integer. & number of players.
		-v    X	: Verbosity levels
			- 0 : Show only essentials
			- 1 : Show lives
			- 2 : Show cycles
			- 4 : Show operations
			- 8 : Show deaths
			- 16 : Show cycles to die
